e still delivering a quality experience.</p>
<p>The existing programs vary in content and duration of time abroad. Some are designed to be an excursion of a few weeks, visiting as many sites as possible, while others are full academic semesters, wherein students actually attend universities abroad. For details about specific programs, take a look the links in the column to the left.</p>
<p>In addition to programs offered at BYU-Idaho, BYU-Idaho students are welcome to apply to BYU Kennedy Center International Study Programs. A link to their homepage can also be found in the left-side column.</p>
